tool_description:
A specialized tool designed for efficiently providing real-time data from aviator (crash game) websites.

This API-driven solution automates the processing of gathering aviator payouts so that you can know exactly when and where to bet.
name: Aviator Scrapper API
title: Aviator Scrapper API

api_list.name: Check Casinobit Health Status
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://aviator-scrapper-api.p.rapidapi.com/api/apps/casinobit/health/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "aviator-scrapper-api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
